OL,3,CScottish budget to pass first vote at
OL,4,CHolyrood
OL,6,FThe Scottish Government's tax and
OL,7,Fspending plans for this year will pass
OL,8,Ftheir first hurdle at Holyrood.
OL,10,FThe Greens, the Liberal Democrats and
OL,11,FAlba will back the SNPs budget and
OL,12,FScottish Labour MSPs will abstain.
OL,13,FOnly the Scottish Conservatives will
OL,14,Fvote against.
OL,16,FThe Finance Secretary has said
OL,17,Ftackling child poverty is the
OL,18,Fgovernment's 'top priority'.
