OL,6,FAround one in four children in
OL,7,FDumfries and Galloway is living in
OL,8,Fpoverty.
OL,10,FChild Poverty (figures from Aberlour):
OL,12,FThis budget includes funding to set up
OL,13,Fa Scottish payment to mitigate the
OL,14,Fimpact of the UK Government's two-
OL,15,Fchild cap on benefits from next year.
OL,16,FThe cap limits payments for families
OL,17,Fin receipt of universal credit who
OL,18,Fhave more than two children.
