OL,6,FDawn Ward, the director for children
OL,7,Fand families at Aberlour children's
OL,8,Fcharity, said she would like to see
OL,9,Fthat delivered 'quicker'.
OL,11,F"We know that families need support,
OL,12,Fwe know that they need that now and
OL,13,Fwhilst we know that when that's
OL,14,Fimplemented that will lift 15,000
OL,15,Fchildren out of poverty, those
OL,16,Fchildren need that support right now."
OL,18,FOther measures to address child
OL,19,Fpoverty in the budget include:
