OL,6,FOver recent months, his team has
OL,7,Fnegotiated the support of the Greens,
OL,8,Fthe Liberal Democrats and Alba's Ash
OL,9,FRegan. All are claiming to have won
OL,10,Fbig but in reality they have settled
OL,11,Ffor relatively small concessions in
OL,12,Fexchange for their votes.
OL,14,FThe Greens have secured free school
OL,15,Fmeals for S1 to S3 pupils in receipt
OL,16,Fof the Scottish child payment in eight
OL,17,Fcouncil areas. The budget already
OL,18,Fexpands them to P6 and 7s who are
OL,19,Feligible but this falls short of the
OL,20,Fdemands of many poverty campaigners.
