OL,6,FThe Greens had been critical of the
OL,7,FScottish Government's decision last
OL,8,Fyear to backtrack on their promise to
OL,9,Frollout free school meals to all
OL,10,Fprimary school children - a
OL,11,Fcornerstone of the Greens coalition
OL,12,Fwith the SNP before they were ditched
OL,13,Fby Humza Yousaf last April.
OL,15,FThe bargaining power of the opposition
OL,16,Fparties was weakened early last month
OL,17,Fthough when the Scottish Labour leader
OL,18,FAnas Sarwar surprised commentators by
OL,19,Fannouncing his MSPs would abstain on
OL,20,Fthe vote, allowing it to pass without
OL,21,Fthe need for any opposition votes.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
