OL,6,FHe's been in a particularly awkward
OL,7,Fposition over the budget after the
OL,8,FFinance Secretary's 'rabbit out the
OL,9,Fhat' was a promise to mitigate the two-
OL,10,Fchild benefit cap. It's a move widely
OL,11,Fbacked by poverty campaigners who
OL,12,Fpredict it will lift 15,000 children
OL,13,Fout of poverty.
