OL,6,FThe Labour government at Westminster
OL,7,Fhas repeatedly said they cannot afford
OL,8,Fto lift the cap - which limits the
OL,9,Fpayments families with more than two
OL,10,Fchildren receive. Anas Sarwar has said
OL,11,Fhe wants it scrapped and his MSPs will
OL,12,Fnot stop that progressing by voting
OL,13,Fagainst the budget.
OL,15,FAnd he's gone further, saying he would
OL,16,Fwhip the Scottish Labour group to back
OL,17,Fthe budget if the government brings
OL,18,Fforward the measures to mitigate it to
OL,19,Fthis year. John Swinney has said he
OL,20,Fwould go faster if he could but that
OL,21,Ftimescale seems unlikely.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
