OL,6,FTo deliver the policy the Scottish
OL,7,Fgovernment will need to work with the
OL,8,FUK government. The Department of Work
OL,9,Fand Pensions holds the data they say
OL,10,Fthey need to identify which families
OL,11,Fare affected. This year's budget also
OL,12,Fonly contains the money to set up the
OL,13,Fmechanism to make such payments, it
OL,14,Fdoesn't contain the funding for the
OL,15,Fmeasures which the Scottish Fiscal
OL,16,FCommission estimates would cost #155m
OL,17,Fin 2026-27.
